# Authors & Contributors

Encore is a fork of Theatre.js. The vast majority of this codebase was written
by the Theatre.js authors and contributors listed below. We are grateful for
their work.

## Theatre.js — original authors

- Aria Minaei — creator and lead author <aria@theatrejs.com>
- Andrew Prifer — author of theatric (now @encorejs/tweak), co-author of r3f
- TheaterJS Oy

